        <abstract> 
<p>Congratulates CD on testimonials from the savants of Germany and the Netherlands [<hi rend="italic">Nature</hi> 15 (1877): 356, 410–12] and generally on his contributions to biology.</p>  
<p>Asks if and when CD’s "Variability of organic beings in a state of nature", as projected in 1868 [see <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> 1: 4] is to appear.</p> 
        </abstract>
